{"tid":2479143,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"【南征聯合】《病港ＩＩ》（２ ７）","createTime":"2021-04-07T15:04:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T15:20:16.000Z","uid":26001,"like":84,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d19c42f4ec4f69ba373fb2b322d8b38e81848c6e","tid":2479143,"uid":26001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:04:07.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yQEGr1J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyQEGr1J.jpg&h=e18385b4&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n<p class=\"center\">由於本系列第一季字數超過一百萬字，強烈建議想要追看的讀者，先在紙言閱讀《病港》故事：</p><br />\n<p class=\"center\"><a href=\"https://www.shikoto.com/articles/140642.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shikoto.com%2Farticles%2F140642.html&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYWt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=ace44b96\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.shikoto.com/articles/140642.html</a></p><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/093Th82.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F093Th82.jpg&h=45652fb7&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n<p class=\"center\">廣告</p><br />\n<p class=\"center\">第一季《病港》，一至八冊全數在書局上架，如無法買到個別冊數，可到HKTVmall或是豐林文化Facebook專頁進行網上購買。</p><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<p class=\"center\">有興趣留意我最新消息同動向，歡迎Follow同讚好：</p><br />\nＩＧ：ｍａｋｓｙｕｔ２００３０１６４<br />\nＦＢ：墨說<br />\n紙言：<a href=\"https://www.shikoto.com/authors/2208.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shikoto.com%2Fauthors%2F2208.html&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYWt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=ff9f3723\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.shikoto.com/authors/2208.html</a><br />\nPenana：<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/93168/%E5%A2%A8%E8%AA%AA/stream?fromsearch=%E5%A2%A8%E8%AA%AA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F93168%2F%25E5%25A2%25A8%25E8%25AA%25AA%2Fstream%3Ffromsearch%3D%25E5%25A2%25A8%25E8%25AA%25AA&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYWt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=b2d10112\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/93168/%E5%A2%A8%E8%AA%AA/stream?fromsearch=%E5%A2%A8%E8%AA%AA</a><br />\n第二季病港（準備印刷中）<br />\n酒店故（設計封面中）<br />\n小松女童軍故（修繕中）<br />\n現正籌備階段，預計將在未來幾個月內推出。<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tj9S4ub.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTj9S4ub.jpg&h=7e8bf888&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<p class=\"center\">【《病港日報》資訊區】：</p><br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y8xGaYq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy8xGaYq.png&h=6c7b3c8a&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ARxThN4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FARxThN4.png&h=a285b041&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<p class=\"center\">【Ｍ】</p><br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kixYBy4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkixYBy4.jpg&h=f9403b95&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n【松木村「大師匠」認可神器】：<br />\n１：鯨牙大劍<br />\n２：金鷹頭拐杖<br />\n３：夜行傘<br />\n４：黃金貝果<br />\n５：「七傘系列」<br />\n６：腦電波情緒控制器<br />\n７：巨商之戒<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<p class=\"center\">如果想支持我創作，或者想睇《病港ＩＩ》快少少嘅話，可以到本人以下付費網站購買通行證：</p><br />\n<p class=\"center\"><a href=\"https://maksyut.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmaksyut.com%2F&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYWt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=1b2ed637\" target=\"_blank\">https://maksyut.com/</a></p><br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cLKCKRk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcLKCKRk.gif&h=52c3f268&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"gold\"><strong>連登每有２００正評，付費網站和連登都會加一更，約３０００字</strong></span></p>"},{"pid":"c544f539878dc580d7025f84149f1ee040a6a0d2","tid":2479143,"uid":26001,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:04:23.000Z","msg":"我知病獵們心情緊張，但他們都沒有表露到臉上，還一邊收拾物品，一邊跟戰友有說有笑。<br />\n<br />\n或許這幾個月來，他們練成了一顆鐵血精神。<br />\n<br />\n來到病獵營這一趟，我不急於離開，有時間逐一審視整個營地的架構，順便知悉前副會長的秦狩，是如何管理南征部隊。<br />\n<br />\n秦狩管理方式是軍事化，上大事小務，下至日常生活全都統一，需要跟隨他定下的軍規，沒有例外，沒有特權。<br />\n<br />\n這種管理方式可以把人的紀律性、執行力和團隊精神大大加強，因為大家活在同一個規範下，眾人自然會成為一體。<br />\n<br />\n高效率的戰鬥人員，就是這樣鍊成。<br />\n<br />\n南淵七病獵作為營地權力最高人員，責任自是不輕。<br />\n<br />\n竹三草，教導各種遠程武器、藥物和暗器，包括藥品和不同的箭矢使用方法。<br />\n<br />\n元蒼，教導如何使用盾牌，比如方陣和前線推擠時機的教學。<br />\n<br />\n石在陽，教導使用各種近戰武器，十八般兵器都能請教他。<br />\n<br />\n范世京，教導團隊之間的合作和協調，例如哪一種陣式，可以有效對抗某種特定病者。<br />\n<br />\n姜河冥，教導病者學的進階知識，諸如佔高打低、尋找突破點、錘鉆戰術、牽制攻擊、鉗形攻勢、縱深防禦、楔形陣等進攻戰術和防守戰術。<br />\n<br />\n聶一凜，他可能不善於和人溝通，因此秦狩並沒讓他成為教官，而是審核病獵實力是否足夠的考官，不合資格者將會被趕出病獵營外。他們貴精不貴多，在命懸一線的戰場上，寧願少一個人，都不要一個豬隊友。<br />\n<br />\n他每天都會站在競技場上，給予任何一位病獵挑戰，如果勝出的話可獲得肉罐頭一個。<br />\n<br />\n因此，就算實力差距像鴻溝巨大，仍然會有病獵樂於不疲地挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n場上用到的武器雖是木製，但聽聞聶一凜還是會把每個挑戰者打得狼狽不堪。"},{"pid":"c0430cdbc06dfe57e331e5de2db28f99d94fe0ef","tid":2479143,"uid":38793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:04:31.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"4dfa283f549ad00202681ed0816b34149c6cd20b","tid":2479143,"uid":26001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:04:33.000Z","msg":"最後，是掌握病獵營最高權力的秦狩，他是象徵住南征戰爭的人物，名高天下的病獵老兵，只要有他存在，病獵就會士氣莫名大增，屬病獵協會的元老級人物，亦是指揮官。<br />\n<br />\n我越是審視，越覺得自己沒有做錯第二次南征戰爭的決定。<br />\n<br />\n用一百多名病獵的生命，來換取他們七個人性命，回報將會是無可估量。<br />\n<br />\n我見病獵營的部隊還要準備一段時間，自己便先行下山。<br />\n<br />\n時間尚早，我一回城便再到管理人辦公室，看看頹廢的王達尼。<br />\n<br />\n他由今早伏桌睡眠，變成捲縮身子，打側睡於沙發上。<br />\n<br />\n管理人的位置，則變成小老鼠寶拉坐著。<br />\n<br />\n她正使用帳簿，核著密密麻麻的數字。<br />\n<br />\n「咣──」她見我入了來，才停下計算。<br />\n<br />\n「你係之前嗰個&hellip;&hellip;」寶拉似乎認得我。<br />\n<br />\n我點點頭：「酒吧。」<br />\n<br />\n寶拉確認過眼神後，問：「你識唔識洗黑籽。」<br />\n<br />\n「洗黑籽？」是洗黑錢的意思嗎&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n「總之洗錢，你知唔知邊到可以一次過，洗走一大筆錢。」<br />\n<br />\n「點會唔識。」<br />\n<br />\n「我唔識，仲係嚟咗無幾耐，其他倖存區都無參觀過，對依到唔係好熟，既然我諗你都係佬大朋友，你可以幫個手洗黑錢？」寶拉竟然這樣問。<br />\n<br />\n「你去拍賣行應該可以&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n「依到有拍賣行？」寶拉抬起頭。<br />\n<br />\n「有，銅鑼灣嗰邊。」<br />\n<br />\n「好&hellip;&hellip;」她似乎有著什麼計劃。<br />\n<br />\n「點解要洗黑錢。」我好奇問她。<br />\n<br />\n「我哋秘密搞嘅煙酒收益，全部都同財務報表唔同，唔可以俾政府查到我哋收埋咗咁多利潤無報到，啲錢要洗去保值嘅物品到。」寶拉簡單解釋。<br />\n<br />\n「明&hellip;&hellip;」我似懂非懂。"},{"pid":"fb8b3c79f1f90740a355c0a0f7bd8305338a5e38","tid":2479143,"uid":79700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:04:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/miracle_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f20c6083176813494dcd0902f02408d73e7dbbb","tid":2479143,"uid":16468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:04:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />留名 正評"},{"pid":"15c0ebef8ec7e0096290e10e0bbe299251f59bfe","tid":2479143,"uid":187274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:04:43.000Z","msg":"正皮先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e658a83dbe1c273dd5eba023c3da7e83a26ea2e5","tid":2479143,"uid":26001,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:04:44.000Z","msg":"「所以，你可以幫手？買古董、買車、買樓隨得你&hellip;&hellip;」寶拉說。<br />\n<br />\n「好遺憾，我幫唔到。」<br />\n<br />\n「嗯？」寶拉瞇眼看我。<br />\n<br />\n「我俾成個夕鯨國當咗係死人，啲人認到我會通緝返去。」我直說。<br />\n<br />\n寶拉細細想一想，又提出：「咁不如我去買嘢，你幫我睇住呢到先。」<br />\n<br />\n「睇、睇住？我唔識計數&hellip;&hellip;」我看到帳簿只有燒掉它的念頭。<br />\n<br />\n「你唔洗識睇數，幫手處理下問題就得。」寶拉站起，想快點起行。<br />\n<br />\n「咩問題。」<br />\n<br />\n「你坐我個位先。」寶拉把大班椅讓給我坐。<br />\n<br />\n我無牽掛的躺到椅背，多少都明白到王達尼無心工作的原因。<br />\n<br />\n「你仲未講係咩問題。」坐下後，我追問寶拉。<br />\n<br />\n「依到係個問題城市，大把有問題嘅人會嚟搵你。」寶拉說完這句，便推開大門：「啊&hellip;&hellip;你有冇咩係想要。」<br />\n<br />\n「想要？」<br />\n<br />\n不知怎地，我無故想起今早《病港日報》上的報導，說銅鑼灣等下會有音樂會，而獎品是一份珍貴的琴譜。<br />\n<br />\n「《憂月》，係今日銅鑼灣音樂大賽嘅獎品嚟。」我說。<br />\n<br />\n「嗯&hellip;&hellip;」寶拉真的離開了。<br />\n<br />\n沒辦法，即管坐坐，當作看顧一下王達尼就好。<br />\n<br />\n原本我以為是件容易的差事，想不到問題很快就找上門了&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n「暫代管理人，有兩位先生想你評下理，你要唔要見下佢哋？」<br />\n<br />\n「評理？」<br />\n<br />\n「佢哋似乎有少少紛爭&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n「叫佢哋入嚟。」<br />\n<br />\n不一會，兩名已到中年的男子，手中握著一根煙來到我面前，那根煙他們一人握頭，另一人握尾，情況有點奇怪。<br />\n<br />\n「兩位，請問發生咩事？」我了當地問。<br />\n<br />\nA君：「我係街上執到枝煙頭，條友就話係佢見到先嘅！」<br />\n<br />\nB君：「咩呀！咁真係我見到先喎，你都係後尾先執。」<br />\n<br />\nA君：「咁咪係我囉。」<br />\n<br />\nB君：「總之係我隻眼望到先&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n我：「咁到底你兩個爭咩呢。」<br />\n<br />\n兩人同時說：「爭呢枝煙囉！」<br />\n<br />\n不是吧？兩個大男人為了根掉落地上的煙頭，而特意找上了來管理人辦公室&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n「你哋用國際慣例猜包剪揼自己解決，唔好浪費我寶貴嘅時間。」我讓他們兩個離開。<br />\n<br />\n緊接下來，都是些無聊的事情，我才知道管理人其中一份工作，是解決市民的問題。<br />\n<br />\n例如，有位母親抱著小嬰兒到來，因為生孩子了而要求我派錢，還有各式各樣奇葩的一系列問題，於是我採取跟王達尼一樣的政策了，讓女秘書不要再放人入來。"},{"pid":"4327abb7f74c541b0a9cece50a23ff59513c894a","tid":2479143,"uid":246369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:04:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e0c8a453c30d6890fd3deb3eead91246361930","tid":2479143,"uid":22450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:05:01.000Z","msg":"留名一身蟻"},{"pid":"68fd303b6b75a486cf6139ae6bdb1097e38d5666","tid":2479143,"uid":71960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:05:05.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a94aba7613cd557edac901da85923b8ea5b89ce","tid":2479143,"uid":139644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:05:25.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afae5de596ae168c3c0b9d8bfa90e53be5ad9f37","tid":2479143,"uid":124262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:05:28.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"ceb561812cb24fe82c4fc44b14843bfc86f13b7b","tid":2479143,"uid":251284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:06:10.000Z","msg":"我愛墨b<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df82ff7093ebaecd9285fda8c5d43d75a333912","tid":2479143,"uid":356039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:06:28.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"3fd45dda741ce6c628d4a27f8d97f582664a5028","tid":2479143,"uid":216695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:07:21.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/vampire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2b8dbe2a8e720a4af8a6ad9adb422a7fca9bccb","tid":2479143,"uid":53349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:08:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheerleading.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheerleading.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheerleading.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f08f099eee96e2cff88248037df8e9c17a727603","tid":2479143,"uid":251284,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:08:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>現正籌備階段，預計將在未來幾個月內推出。</blockquote><br />\n二、三月變未來幾個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3e64af4cc953f64e056ff1b9bb682ca607ed1e3","tid":2479143,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:09:54.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"8dfd796997d17a19993e16cc3c8affd6805d72c8","tid":2479143,"uid":251284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:10:41.000Z","msg":"記得補上上個post 800<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c756f06c599cbdf6c6a04319668166e4ea5d666","tid":2479143,"uid":304431,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:12:32.000Z","msg":"【南征聯合】《病港ＩＩ》（８）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2138457\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2138457</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be667e838cd76ffc46aa6f6b534544f7c955ced2","tid":2479143,"uid":35572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:12:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f84e692294049d00f8c9d18f1828116434e63eec","tid":2479143,"uid":89170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:13:41.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"12ca408267d3545d2288bc96a76a736cc9f4e352","tid":2479143,"uid":251284,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8c756f06c599cbdf6c6a04319668166e4ea5d666","tid":2479143,"uid":304431,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:12:32.000Z","msg":"【南征聯合】《病港ＩＩ》（８）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2138457\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2138457</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:15:21.000Z","msg":"重複topic咁失策<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"987a53a5c3c9d79cb89152fe3d440fccc9888105","tid":2479143,"uid":21982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:17:20.000Z","msg":"Lm <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheerleading.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheerleading.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheerleading.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}